data.description: Welcome to 6620 Cascade Drive in the Sendero Springs neighborhood and highly sought-after Midway ISD school district. This spacious, single story home has 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and over 2,200 square feet. The front entryway leads you to an open concept living space with raised ceilings, a corner wood burning fireplace and formal dining area. Storage and prep space are abundant in the eat-in kitchen with a generous pantry, island, and beautiful cabinetry with granite countertops. You will appreciate the isolated primary-suite that features a sitting area and tray ceilings. Spend fall evenings on the covered screened-in back patio. Convenient location for your daily commute. Minutes away from IH-35, Hwy 6, Baylor Scott & White Hospital, Central Texas Marketplace and so much more! Don't forget to ask about the $5,000 seller's credit. Call today to schedule your showing.
